properties.areaDesc: Chesapeake Bay from Sandy Point to North Beach MD; Chesapeake Bay north of Pooles Island MD; Chester River to Queenstown MD; Chesapeake Bay from Drum Point MD to Smith Point VA; Chesapeake Bay from North Beach to Drum Point MD; Eastern Bay; Choptank River to Cambridge MD and the Little Choptank River; Chesapeake Bay from Pooles Island to Sandy Point MD
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 11 at 6:22PM EST until February 12 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Baltimore MD/Washington DC
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 15 kt with gusts up to 20 kt
expected.

* WHERE...Chesapeake Bay main channel north of Smith Point VA,
Chester River to Queenstown MD, Eastern Bay, and Choptank
River to Cambridge MD and the Little Choptank River.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 4 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 4 AM EST WEDNESDAY
